               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar ”Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-191vc)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra-32rc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     32va-60rc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 60ra-91vc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     92ra-127vc) 
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 128ra-166va)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     166vb-191vc) 
 The commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns 
                     
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
