               <provenance>Mazmura Dǝngǝl is mentioned in supplication
                     formulas. In addition, two other persons, Mazmura Māryām (7rc, 34vc) and Mazmura Qāl (139va)
                     are mentioned. Mazmura Dǝngǝl. The Ms. (along with GKM-011)
                     was brought from Gondär by ʾIsāyǝyyās for Mazmura Dǝngǝl (?) and was later
                     donated by the latter to the monastery (s. Additio 2).</provenance></history>
